snippet.title: Best VGM 1066 - Spider-Man & X-Men : Arcade's Revenge - Gambit
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES / Genesis
Spider-Man & X-Men : Arcade's Revenge (1992)
Gambit
Tim Follin & Geoff Follin
